instance.description: Supplementary Figure 1. B2R expression in somatotrophs from the pituitary gland of Drd2 KO and WT mice. Identification of B2R (magenta) and growth hormone (green) by double indirect immunofluorescence in WT female and male pituitary slices (F WT and M WT, respectively) and D2R KO female and male (F KO AND M KO, respectively). Nuclei were counterstained with DAPI (blue). White arrows indicate the co-localization zone.
